- Technical Details
    - Tech Stack:
        - Java
        - Android SDK (minSdk 21, targetSdk 35)
        - OpenGL ES 2.0 for filter rendering
        - Gradle 8.7, AGP 8.6.1
    - Key Files:
        - editor/src/main/java/com/photoeditor/editor/EditorActivity.java: Main editor screen
        - editor/src/main/java/com/photoeditor/editor/filter/FilterRenderer.java: OpenGL rendering pipeline
        - editor/src/main/java/com/photoeditor/editor/filter/FilterShaders.java: GLSL shader code
        - editor/src/main/java/com/photoeditor/editor/crop/CropActivity.java: Crop and rotate screen
        - editor/src/main/java/com/photoeditor/editor/paint/PaintActivity.java: Drawing screen
    - Architecture Notes:
        - Two-module structure: app (thin shell) + editor (library module)
        - Filter pipeline: multi-pass OpenGL (sharpen pass, tools pass, display pass)
        - Crop: Canvas-based with CropAreaView overlay and CropView for pan/zoom
        - Paint: Canvas-based stamp rendering with undo stack
        - Algorithms ported from Telegram (GPL v2)

